<member><link linkend="fundimental">Fundimentals</link></member>
<member><link linkend="Tutorial">Step by Step Tutorial</link></member>
<member><link linkend="KWordScreen">The KWord Screen</link></member>
<member><link linkend="Guides">Document Storage and Printing</link></member>
<member><link linkend="Guides2">Editing Your Document</link></member>
<member><link linkend="menuintro">Introduction to Menu Bars and Tool Bars</link></member>
</simplelist></para></entry></row>
<row><entry>Intermediate</entry><entry>Comfortable with other page based wordprocessors (Microsoft Word, Word Perfect and Applixware.)  </entry>
<entry><para><simplelist type="vert" columns="1">
<member><link linkend="fundimental">Fundimentals</link></member>
<member><link linkend="Tutorial">Step by Step Tutorial</link></member>
</simplelist></para></entry></row>
