</informaltable>

<para>Obviously this will not cover everyones needs.  What I hope it will do,
however, is help you determine which parts of the manual you need to
read before you begin using <application>KWord</application>.</para>

<para>These sections will help you get started initially. You can then refer
to the other parts of this manual as needed to help you with specific
questions or situations.</para>

</sect1>
